# Expanding Cards Project

![Expanding Cards](https://github.com/Anushkarathore07/project--1.git)

## Introduction

The Expanding Cards project is a visually engaging and interactive component for web applications, designed to enhance user experience through dynamic content display. When a user clicks on a card, it expands smoothly, revealing more information.

## Features

- Smooth and responsive animations
- Click-to-expand functionality
- Easy to customize and integrate into existing projects
- Mobile-friendly design
- Lightweight and performant

## Technologies Used

- HTML
- CSS
- JavaScript (or mention any specific libraries/frameworks used)

## Installation

To set up this project locally, follow these steps:

1. **Clone the repository:**

   ```sh
   git clone https://github.com/Anushkarathore07/Project---1.git
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Usage
Open index.html in a web browser to see the expanding cards in action.
Click on any card to expand it and reveal more information.
Click on the expanded card to collapse it back to its original state.
